OL,7,FA pivotal figure of the Welsh Miners'
OL,8,FStrike says the squabbling between the
OL,9,FUK and Welsh Governments over is
OL,10,Falienating people from politics.
OL,12,FSian James, a former Labour MP and a
OL,13,Fcommunity organiser during the 1984
OL,14,Fstrikes, says "There's no need to ask
OL,15,Fwhy people have lost faith in
OL,16,Fpoliticians."
