OL,7,FShe was responding to a question on Y
OL,8,FByd yn ei Le on S4C about the
OL,9,Faccusations from both governments that
OL,10,Fthe other hadn't done enough to
OL,11,Fsupport TATA's workers.
OL,13,FThe First Minister Mark Drakeford has
OL,14,Faccused Prime Minister Rishi Sunak of
OL,15,Frefusing to take a call from him to
OL,16,Fdiscuss TATA's plans to cut 2,800 jobs
OL,17,F- while the Welsh Secretary David TC
OL,18,FDavies has accused the First Minister
OL,19,Fof ignoring his offer of a call.
