OL,3,C'We don't have confidence in our
OL,4,Ccommunities anymore that jobs will
OL,5,Ccome'
OL,7,FSian James said the announcement of
OL,8,Fthe job cuts in the iconic steel plant
OL,9,Fin Port Talbot had sent a "shiver
OL,10,Fthrough the community."
OL,12,FRecalling the demise of the Welsh
OL,13,Fvalleys following coal tip closures in
OL,14,Fthe 80s, Sian James said the recent
OL,15,Fannouncement was "so similar."
OL,17,F"We know through experience what the
OL,18,Fend of that (coal pit closure) journey
OL,19,Fwas - losing 23,000 jobs."
